description:
Meet the collaboration pack between 「Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL」 and AfreecaTV's virtual BJ crew 'POCOTONE'!
This DLC includes a total of 10 new songs.

New Songs:
1. Flower Garden - STELLAR (Arr. STELLAR, N4ML) / Voc. YAM
2. Dream Star -  STELLAR / Voc. Hiyoko, YAM
3. I Love Me - litmus* / Voc. Hiyoko
4. Scatter One's Consolation - 139cm (Arr. litmus*) / Voc. Origgung
5. Come to an End - 139cm (Arr. STELLAR) / Voc. YAM
6. Cosmic Telepathy - N4ML / Voc. Origgung, Hiyoko, YAM
7. :heart: :mag: :rainbow: :duck: :sparkles: - 139cm / Voc. Origgung
8. Love this memory - 139cm / Voc. Origgung, Hiyoko, YAM
9. First love begins - STELLAR / Voc. Hiyoko
10. Disallowed – BlueArpeggio / Voc. Origgung, Hiyoko
